senses
  entry
    definition "the actions and activities assigned to or required or expected of a person or group"
    examples ("the function of a teacher" "the government must do its part" "play its role")
    id oewn-00721817-n
    partOfSpeech n
    synonyms (function office part)
  entry
    definition "an actor's portrayal of someone in a play"
    examples ("she played the part of Desdemona")
    id oewn-05937794-n
    partOfSpeech n
    synonyms (character "theatrical role" part persona)
  entry
    definition "what something is used for"
    examples ("the function of an auger is to bore holes" "ballet is beautiful but what use is it?")
    id oewn-05156572-n
    partOfSpeech n
    synonyms (function purpose use)
  entry
    definition "normal or customary activity of a person in a particular social setting"
    examples ("what is your role on the team?")
    id oewn-00723312-n
    partOfSpeech n
source "oewn:2024"
